This is a '''list of national parks in [[Albania]]''' which includes 14 [[national park]]s and a [[marine park]].<ref>{{cite web|title=PËRSHKRIMI I RRJETIT AKTUAL TË ZONAVE TË MBROJTURA|url=http://www.mjedisi.gov.al/files/userfiles/Biodiversiteti/ZM&PK-Pershkrim.pdf|website=mjedisi.gov.al|language=Albanian|format=PDF}}</ref> They cover a surface area of {{convert|210668.48|hectare|km2|}} or roughly 6.7% of the overall territory. The national policy for governing and management of the national parks is implemented by the [[Ministry of Environment (Albania)|Ministry of Environment of Albania]].

